Privacy Policy:
At Amwaj Alwaha, we take the privacy of our application users seriously.
This policy outlines the information we collect, how we use it, and how we protect your personal information. By using our application, you agree to this policy.
Information We Collect:
When using our application,
we may collect the following information:- Your device location for displaying nearby branches and providing other location-dependent services.\n- Your device ID to enable us to provide personalized services to you.
-Your login information if you use the login feature to manage users and branches.
- Other information provided by you, such as feedback and inquiries.
How We Use Your Information:We use the information we collect to provide you with application services,
improve application functionality, and communicate with you regarding updates and new features.
We do not share your personal information with third parties unless required by law or necessary for providing application services to you.
How We Protect Your Information:We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, and destruction. However, we cannot guarantee the security of your personal information transmitted through the application.
Changes to this Policy:
We may update this policy from time to time.
We encourage you to review this policy periodically for any changes
